item.title: CVE-2023-32114|2024-09-28T21:56:20.581Z -- sap_se -- sap%20netweaver%20%28change%20and%20transport%20system%29
item.description: SAP NetWeaver (Change and Transport System) - versions 702, 731, 740, 750, 751, 752, 753, 754, 755, 756, 757, allows an authenticated user with admin privileges to maliciously run a benchmark program repeatedly in intent to slowdown or make the server unavailable which may lead to a limited impact on Availability with No impact on Confidentiality and Integrity of the application.
